[SN]TITLE[SN]
Nice attack: NI woman describes attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A Northern Ireland woman has described the scenes she witnessed on Thursday night in Nice.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
15 July 2016 Last updated at 17:12 BST
Laura McGarity told the BBC the attacks will not stop her from staying in the French city for the rest of her holiday.
At least 84 people were killed when a lorry deliberately crashed into a crowd of people on the Promenade des Anglais on Thursday night.
